esday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATCA%20and%20Daniels%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20a%20comment%2C%20sent%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-airport-flight-delays-cancellations-government-shutdown-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762028174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690667ff0be9845f2dc58c0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-airport-flight-delays-cancellations-government-shutdown-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cancellation%20rates%20are%20high%20at%20airports%20in%20the%20New%20York%20metro%20region%2C%20including%20LaGuardia%2C%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20and%20Newark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi%2CTaylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-airport-flight-delays-cancellations-government-shutdown-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nearly%2065%2C000%20kids%20could%20lose%20access%20to%20Head%20Start%20programs%20if%20the%20government%20shutdown%20continues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Top-down%20view%20of%20preschool%20kids%20using%20beads%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690507b7599d46a4ccc143de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENationwide%2C%20almost%2065%2C000%20children%20at%20140%20Head%20Start%20programs%20face%20a%20funding%20lapse%20and%20may%20lose%20access%20as%20of%20Monday.%3Cp%3ELordn%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHead%20Start%20programs%20are%20facing%20closures%20due%20to%20a%20federal%20funding%20lapse%20amid%20the%20government%20shutdown.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20shutdown%20affects%20nearly%2065%2C000%20children%20and%20over%2022%2C000%20staff%20nationwide%20in%20Head%20Start.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrograms%20rely%20on%20federal%20grants%20for%2080%25%20of%20funding%2C%20with%20some%20using%20credit%20to%20stay%20open.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhead-start-childcare-centers-cant-get-federal-funds-pay-employees-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHead%20Start%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20country%20won't%20open%20their%20doors%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2065%2C000%20children%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnhsa.org%2Fabout-nhsa%2Fnewsroom%2Fstatements%2Fstate-by-state-how-the-shutdown-impacts-head-start%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHead%20Start%20programs%20nationwide%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20lose%20access%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20after%20missing%20their%20November%201%20funding%20deadline%20for%20federal%20grants%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20government%20shutdown%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Head%20Start%20Association.%20Over%2022%2C000%20staff%20at%20these%20centers%20are%20also%20at%20risk%20of%20losing%20their%20jobs%20or%20being%20furloughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHead%20Start%20is%20a%20federally%20funded%20program%20that%20provides%20childcare%20and%20early%20education%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fheadstart.gov%2Fprogram-data%2Farticle%2Fhead-start-program-facts-fiscal-year-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%20715%2C000%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20low-income%20families%2C%20from%20birth%20to%20age%205.%20Those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fheadstart.gov%2Fhow-apply%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeligible%20for%20Head%20Start%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20families%20who%20already%20rely%20on%20public%20assistance%20programs%2C%20such%20as%20SNAP%2C%20or%20who%20fall%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamilies%20could%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnhsa.org%2Fabout-nhsa%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fnhsa-calls-congress-to-end-federal-shutdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20without%20childcare%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20their%20Head%20Start%20programs%20lose%20funding.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20scary%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tommy%20Sheridan%2C%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Head%20Start%20Association.%20%26quot%3BHead%20Start%20is%20preschool%20services%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20than%20just%20what%20we%20think%20of%20as%20traditional%20preschool.%20It%20is%20oftentimes%20the%20only%20place%20that%20children%20get%20access%20to%20nutritious%20meals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20centers%20nationwide%20may%20shut%20their%20doors%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffhsa.memberclicks.net%2Fnearly-9-000-florida-children-and-families-could-lose_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efurlough%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20others%20have%20already%20created%20contingency%20plans%20to%20stay%20open%20temporarily.%20They've%20reached%20for%20rainy%20day%20funds%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fckcac.org%2Fnewsletter%2Ffor-immediate-release10-28-25-ckcac-head-start-early-head-start-will-remain-open-on-november-3rd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaken%20out%20lines%20of%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20had%20philanthropic%20donors%20support%20the%20programs%20families%20and%20staff%20rely%20on%20for%20childcare%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20grants%20can%20account%20for%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fheadstart.gov%2Ffiscal-management%2Farticle%2Fnon-federal-match-narrative%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E80%25%20of%20a%20Head%20Start%20program's%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20these%20funds%20essential%20to%20its%20continued%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Conover%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Central%20Kentucky%20Community%20Action%20Council%20(CKCAC)%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20agency%20aiding%20residents%20through%20programs%20and%20services%2C%20said%20he%20and%20his%20team%20are%20taking%20out%20a%20%241%20million%20line%20of%20credit%20to%20keep%20early%20education%20centers%20open.%20They%20are%20hoping%20the%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20will%20reimburse%20these%20interim%20expenses%20and%20provide%20back%20pay%20to%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConover%20is%20in%20central%20Kentucky%2C%20and%20the%20nine%20centers%20he%20oversees%2C%20along%20with%20other%20services%20for%20low-income%20families%2C%20are%20set%20to%20stay%20open%20until%20November%2021.%20The%20centers%20serve%20400%20students%20they%20teach%20and%20they%20employ%20150%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHead%20Start%20programs%20receive%20annual%20federal%20grants%20for%20the%20coming%20year's%20funding%2C%20and%20with%20the%20shutdown%20underway%2C%20November%20grantees%20have%20no%20guidance.%20About%20140%20centers%2C%20or%2010%25%20of%20Head%20Start%20programs%20nationwide%2C%20are%20November%20grantees%20and%20are%20set%20to%20not%20get%20their%20funding%20renewed%20amid%20the%20shutdown.%20Conover%20described%20the%20situation%20as%20%26quot%3Bdumb%20luck%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20shutdown%20to%20fall%20in%20this%20year%2C%20in%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20programs%20receive%20funding%20at%20different%20times%20throughout%20the%20year.%20While%20some%20centers%20received%20funding%20before%20October%201%2C%20the%20longer%20the%20shutdown%20lasts%2C%20the%20more%20people%20are%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ripple%20effects%20of%20this%20shutdown%20may%20not%20be%20huge%20right%20now%2C%20but%20the%20longer%20they%20go%2C%20the%20bigger%20the%20ripples%20become%2C%26quot%3B%20Conover%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Indiana%2C%20Rhett%20Cecil%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Indiana%20Head%20Start%20Association%2C%20said%20that%20Indiana%20has%202%2C662%20student%20slots%20at%20risk%20without%20funding%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20nearly%20850%20staff%20members.%20Indiana%20had%20almost%2013%2C000%20kids%20enrolled%20last%20year%20and%20employed%204%2C000%20people%20at%20Head%20Start%20programs%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20almost%2075%25%20of%20the%20families%20enrolled%20in%20Head%20Start%20programs%20have%20both%20parents%20working.%20Without%20reliable%20childcare%20options%2C%20they%20must%20weigh%20the%20decision%20between%20going%20to%20work%20and%20caring%20for%20their%20young%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%201%2C700%20families%20that%20are%20going%20to%20have%20to%20make%20the%20decision%20starting%20on%20Monday%3A%20Do%20I%20go%20to%20work%20or%20do%20I%20take%20care%20of%20my%20children%3F%26quot%3B%20Cecil%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20said%20once%20the%20government%20reopens%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20Head%20Start%20(OHS)%20will%20award%20grants%20scheduled%20for%20October%201%20and%20November%201%20to%20programs.%20They%20said%20grantees%20can%20then%20expect%20direct%20communication%20with%20OHS%20regarding%20a%20timeline%20for%20the%20arrival%20of%20federal%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECecil%2C%20Conover%2C%20and%20Sheridan%20all%20said%20they%20have%20contacted%20local%2C%20state%2C%20and%20federal%20government%20officials%20and%20haven't%20received%20guidance%20on%20funding.%20Cecil%20said%20he's%20still%20%26quot%3Bwaiting%20for%20that%20magic%20email%26quot%3B%20to%20let%20him%20know%20funding%20is%20back%20to%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Akin%2C%20the%20director%20of%20Head%20Start%20at%20the%20Central%20Kentucky%20Community%20Action%20Council%2C%20said%20she%20and%20her%20team%20have%20aimed%20to%20clearly%20communicate%20with%20parents%20who%20are%20in%20limbo%20for%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20unsure%20where%20their%20children%20will%20attend%20during%20the%20day%20after%20the%20November%2021%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%