%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69050c1b0be9845f2dc58480%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221154%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECopeland%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20John%2C%20inside%20their%2018-feet-by-8-feet%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Melanie%20Copeland%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I'm%20naturally%20inclined%20toward%20mechanics.%20My%20sister%20was%20usually%20the%20one%20throwing%20the%20doll's%20tea%20party%20when%20we%20were%20little%2C%20while%20I%20was%20playing%20with%20blocks%20and%20Erector%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workshop%20was%20completely%20hands-on%2C%20and%20although%20we%20made%20mistakes%20at%20times%2C%20we%20eventually%20figured%20out%20the%20spacing%20and%20how%20the%20pieces%20are%20put%20together.%20By%20the%20seventh%20day%2C%20before%20the%20hauler%20arrived%20to%20take%20our%20144%20square%20foot%20home%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-living-in-virginia-from-someone-who-left-misses-it-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVirginia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20knew%20it%20wasn't%20rocket%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lived%20in%20a%20friend's%20backyard%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-campground-camper-van-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eat%20a%20campground%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20obtaining%20a%20farm%20loan%20and%20purchasing%20a%201.07-acre%20plot%20of%20land%20for%20%2416%2C000%20in%202000.%20It%20was%20relatively%20cheap%20because%20it%20had%20a%20burned-down%20house%20on%20it%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20clear%20the%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da38672b-8061-41b1-af8b-560fc2fa6649%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20nose%20to%20the%20grindstone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20and%20I%20put%20our%20life%20and%20soul%20into%20the%20property.%20We%20taught%20ourselves%20how%20to%20paint%2C%20stain%2C%20and%20do%20polyurethane%20and%20finishing%20work.%20We%20made%20some%20frustrating%20mistakes%2C%20but%20we%20learned%20and%20continued%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20know%20how%20to%20fix%20everything%20in%20our%20home%20because%20we%20built%20it%20ourselves%20and%20understand%20its%20components.%20You%20could%20call%20it%20skill-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultimate-guide-to-getting-started-in-real-estate-first-year-new-agent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereal%20estate%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20but%20quit%20around%20the%20same%20time%20we%20closed%20on%20our%20new%20land.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20nose%20to%20the%20grindstone%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20lying%20on%20a%20pet%20bed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20fire%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69050c8f599d46a4ccc144c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Copelands'%20dog%2C%20General%20Chaos%2C%20get%20cozy%20next%20to%20the%20fireplace%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Melanie%20Copeland%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20reached%20the%20same%20conclusion%20in%202023%20when%20he%20left%20his%20position%20as%20the%20manager%20of%20a%20parking%20garage.%20By%20then%2C%20we'd%20figured%20out%20that%20we%20could%20live%20in%20the%20tiny%20home%20for%20less%20than%20%24300%20a%20month%2C%20including%20the%20land%20payment%2C%20tax%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20power%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%202024%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20leverage%20our%20newly%20proven%20DIY%20abilities%20and%20launch%20our%20own%20business.%20We%20make%20and%20fix%20things%20for%20other%20people%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221247ccbc-3ad7-4e38-b40f-57be1b96baf3%5C%22%3EWe%20rely%20on%20word%20of%20mouth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20worked%20on%20a%20few%20tiny%20homes%20and%20shed%20conversions.%20But%20it's%20mostly%20regular%20houses.%20We%20just%20finished%20staining%20a%20huge%20deck%2C%20and%20I%20built%20a%20custom%20bookcase%20inside%20a%20beautiful%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhaunted-places-historic-homes-to-visit-ghost-tour-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E18th-century%20house%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20no%20marketing%20budget%20and%20rely%20on%20word%20of%20mouth.%20Last%20year's%20income%20from%20the%20handyman%20business%20was%20%2480%2C000%2C%20and%20we're%20on%20target%20to%20make%20%24100%2C00%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20our%2018ft%20by%208ft%20tiny%20home%20opened%20up%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20for%20us%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20is%20being%20our%20own%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafter-losing-job-built-tiny-home-led-new-career-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762019701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690509540be9845f2dc583fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafter-losing-job-built-tiny-home-led-new-career-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Melanie%20Copeland%20lost%20her%20job%2C%20built%20a%20144-sq-ft%20tiny%20house%2C%20and%20launched%20a%20handyman%20business%20with%20her%20husband%20in%20Virginia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jane%20Ridley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A134%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafter-losing-job-built-tiny-home-led-new-career-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tense%20days%20ahead%20as%20tens%20of%20thousands%20line%20streets%20for%20anniversary%20of%20Novi%20Sad%20tragedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762019460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F11%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-novi-sad-serbia_7068995.jpg%3F20251101175