.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20from%20the%20admiral's%20bridge%20on%20board%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ff9eeac007ca8c2737af96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20the%20admiral's%20bridge.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USS%20New%20Jersey%20measures%2011%20stories%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisible%20across%20the%20Delaware%20River%2C%20the%20Independence%20Seaport%20Museum%20houses%20two%20more%20historic%20vessels%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-warship-history-olympia-tour-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUSS%20Olympia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20oldest%20steep%20warship%20still%20afloat%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-submarine-tour-world-war-ii-becuna-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUSS%20Becuna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20World%20War%20II%20Balao-class%20submarine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20took%20a%20crew%20of%2077%20people%20to%20operate%20the%2016-inch%20guns%20from%20each%20of%20the%20ship's%20three%20gun%20turrets.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Missiles%20on%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffa96fc007ca8c2737b11c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMissiles%20on%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20offers%20special%2090-minute%20in-depth%20tours%20of%20Turret%20II%2C%20spanning%20five%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20plotting%20room%2C%20an%20electromechanical%20analog%20computer%20called%20the%20Mark%208%20Rangekeeper%20was%20used%20to%20aim%20the%2016-inch%20guns.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mark%208%20Rangekeeper%20used%20to%20aim%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey's%2016-inch%20guns.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffacf0c007ca8c2737b1b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mark%208%20Rangekeeper.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mark%208%20Rangekeeper%20could%20calculate%20where%20a%20target%20would%20be%20when%20the%20projectile%20arrived%20while%20accounting%20for%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20Earth's%20rotation%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Coriolis%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USS%20New%20Jersey%20has%20the%20last%20Mark%208%20Rangekeeper%20in%20the%20world%20that%20still%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20favorite%20thing%20about%20the%20computer%20is%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20they%20looked%20at%20replacing%20it%20with%20a%20modern%20digital%20computer%20and%20they%20chose%20not%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Szimanski%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20modern%20computer%20was%20as%20accurate%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20more%20accurate%2C%20so%20why%20waste%20the%20money%3F%20Plus%2C%20if%20we%20lose%20power%20because%20we've%20been%20hit%20by%20the%20enemy%2C%20the%20modern%20computer%20dies.%20This%20one%20has%20a%20hand%20crank%20as%20a%20backup.%20You%20just%20pick%20the%20lowest-ranking%20sailor%20in%20the%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20of%20the%20coolest%20parts%20of%20the%20entire%20tour%20was%20the%20ability%20to%20pull%20the%20trigger%20on%20the%2016-inch%20guns%20with%20booming%20sound%20effects.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Triggers%20for%20the%2016-inch%20guns%20on%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffaf8ac007ca8c2737b201%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETriggers%20for%20the%2016-inch%20guns%20on%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20screen%20also%20showed%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20guns%20firing%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20even%20more%20realistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20record-holding%20length%20of%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey%20became%20apparent%20when%20looking%20down%20Broadway%2C%20the%20ship's%20longest%20passageway.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Broadway%20on%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffb0060be9845f2dc529bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBroadway%20on%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hallway%20featured%20equipment%20such%20as%20oxygen%20breathing%20apparatuses%20and%20doors%20leading%20to%20fire%20rooms%20and%20engine%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20USS%20New%20Jersey%20had%20eight%20boilers%2C%20each%20with%20nine%20burners.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20boiler%20on%20board%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffb3c4c007ca8c2737b2b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20boiler%20on%20board%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fire%20room%2C%20crew%20members%20controlled%20how%20much%20fuel%20was%20being%20pumped%20into%20the%20burners%20by%20changing%20the%20fuel%20nozzles.%20This%20was%20done%20every%20four%20hours%20or%20every%20time%20the%20ship%20changed%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20added%20air%20conditioning%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20ship%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20point%20in%20trying%20to%20cool%20off%20the%20boiler%20room%2C%20which%