3EThe%20startup%20is%20working%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautonomous-vehicle-experts-discuss-scaling-strategies-and-safety-measures-to-accelerate-growth-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efully%20driverless%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20also%20sees%20an%20untapped%20market%20in%20licensing%20supervised%20self-driving%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20a%20demo%20of%20an%20ADAS%20system%20powered%20by%20Wayve's%20AV2.0%20AI%20driver%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20taking%20a%20nearly%20hourlong%20ride%20inside%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-mustang-mach-e-rally-review-ev-suv-off-road-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFord%20Mustang%20Mach-E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20car%20was%20retrofitted%20with%20five%20cameras%2C%20a%20radar%2C%20and%20Wayve's%20AI%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20Wayve%20spokespeople%20joined%20me%20for%20the%20ride%20to%20answer%20questions%20I%20had%20about%20the%20technology%2C%20along%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bvehicle%20safety%20operator%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20behind%20the%20wheel%20in%20case%20he%20had%20to%20intervene%20during%20the%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20it%20reminded%20me%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-experience-human-intervention-incidents-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%20robotaxi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20ride-hailing%20service%20that%20%E2%80%94%20in%20SF%20%E2%80%94%20operates%20with%20a%20safety%20monitor%20behind%20the%20wheel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20with%20Wayve%20didn't%20diminish%20my%20impression%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd-take-rate-model-s-x-vehicles-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla's%20FSD.%3C%2Fa%3E%20However%2C%20it%20did%20raise%20questions%3A%20How%20much%20of%20the%20advantage%20that%20Tesla%20claims%20%E2%80%94%20from%20complete%20software%20ownership%20to%20the%20billions%20of%20miles%20of%20driving%20data%20it%20says%20it%20has%20on%20hand%20%E2%80%94%20ultimately%20matters%20in%20developing%20a%20competent%2C%20assisted%20driving%20system%3F%20How%20long%20will%20it%20take%20for%20Wayve%20to%20catch%20up%3F%20And%2C%20if%20Wayve%20does%2C%20could%20Tesla%20truly%20corner%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-full-self-driving-sales-customers-pay-fsd-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EADAS%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20it's%20still%20only%20thinking%20about%20licensing%20its%20software%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Tesla%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e744c4f-5375-424d-8115-92221d2352d7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Wayve%20approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Tesla%2C%20Wayve%20has%20built%20an%20%26quot%3Bend-to-end%26quot%3B%20AI%20system%2C%20which%20means%20the%20software%20learns%20to%20drive%20directly%20from%20data%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20engineers%20to%20hand-code%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20driver%20scans%20the%20road%20using%20sensors%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20with%20cameras%20only%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-lidar-sensor-versus-cameras-vision-only-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eradar%20and%20lidar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20determines%20how%20to%20steer%20or%20accelerate%20based%20on%20what%20it%20has%20learned%20from%20real-world%20and%20simulated%20driving%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeveraging%20the%20adaptability%20of%20an%20end-to-end%20system%2C%20Wayve%20wants%20to%20distinguish%20itself%20by%20providing%20a%20%26quot%3Bhardware%20agnostic%26quot%3B%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ford%20Mach-E%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69058465599d46a4ccc14a7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWayve%20has%20been%20testing%20its%20AI%20driver%20with%20a%20fleet%20of%20Ford's%20Mustang%20Mach-E%20electric%20vehicle.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20says%20it%20means%20Wayve%20has%20software%20that%20automakers%20could%20plug-and-play%20into%20all%20kinds%20of%20cars%2C%20from%20personally-owned%20vehicles%20to%20commercial%20trucks%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20sensor%20stack%20it%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20OEM%20only%20has%20cameras%2C%20Wayve%20says%20its%20AI%20driver%20will%20work.%20If%20a%20car%20has%20more%20redundant%20sensors%20outside%20of%20cameras%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20AI%20driver%20should%20be%20able%20to%20support%20higher%20levels%20of%20automation%2C%20a%20Wayve%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposition%20to%20automakers%20is%20that%20there%20are%20no%20additional%20hardware%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20integrate%20on%20any%20camera%20or%20sensor%20setup%2C%20on%20any%20system%20or%20chip%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20appealing%20to%20OEMs%20because%20there's%20no%20additional%20hardware%20or%20core%20costs%20or%20CapEx%20on%20their%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272f335b8-f6b0-443f-b449-c374adafa41e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWayve%20chauffeur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20more%20tech%20underlying%20Wayve's%20ADAS%20system%2C%20but%20most%20consumers%20will%20likely%20only%20want%20to%20know%3A%20How%20does%20it%20drive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20demo%20began%20near%20Moscone%20Center%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20South%20of%20Market%20neighborhood%20during%205%20o'clock%20rush%20hour.%20We%20zig-zagged%20through%20the%20city%20for%20a%20few%20miles%20before%20we%20circled%20back%20to%20Moscone%20Center.%20The%2030-minute%20demonstration%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20nearly%20hourlong%20ride%20due%20to%20traffic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20ride%2C%20Wayve%20was%20capable%20of%20stopping%20for%20jaywalking%20pedestrians%20and%20maneuvering%20around%20drivers%20who%20stood%20too%20close%20to%20the%20road%20as%20they%20opened%20their%20car%20doors.%20On%20Mission%20and%206th%2C%20a%20car%20was%20blocking%20the%20intersection%20when%20our%20light%20turned%20green.%20The%20AI%20driver%20still%20waited%20for%20the%20car%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20way%20before%20it%20proceeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20two%20or%20three%20moments%20where%20AV2.0%20braked%20harder%20than%20usual%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20was%20inching%20along%20heavy%20traffic.%20It's%20a%20curious%20behavior%20that%20I've%20noticed%20in%20other%20self-driving%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wayve%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690584a8c007ca8c273812bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20safety%20monitor%20kept%20his%20hands%20close%20to%20the%20wheel%20during%20Wayve's%20demonstration.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20moments%20of%20intervention%20from%20the%20safety%20monitor%20outside%20of%20taking%20over%20to%20park%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Wayve%20spokesperson%20informed%20me%20that%20I%20experienced%20an%20automated%20driving%20level%20that%20falls%20somewhat%20between%20what%20the%20Society%20of%20Automotive%20Engineers%20(SAE)%20labels%20as%20L2%20and%20L3.%20L2%20means%20that%20some%20level%20of%20driving%20is%20automated%2C%20but%20it%20is%20under%20constant%20human%20supervision.%20L3%20is%20when%20a%20car%20can%20drive%20itself%20under%20certain%20conditions%20without%20human%20supervision%20unless%20the%20car%20requests%20the%20driver%20to%20take%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20safety%20operator%20did%20not%20have%20his%20foot%20on%20the%20brakes%2C%20pedal%2C%20or%20steering%20wheel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22289c833d-89f9-4dc2-af4d-3b06dac19eb1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ADAS%20race%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20one-to-one%20comparison%20of%20Tesla's%20technology%20or%20progress%20to%20Wayve's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20experienced%20Wayve's%20AV2.0%20in%20a%20single%2C%20supervised%20demonstration.%20Wayve's%20AI%20driver%20may%20not%20be%20in%20cars%20until%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20can%20go%20buy%20a%20Tesla%20and%20experience%20FSD%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20also%20conducting%20robotaxi%20trials%20without%20a%20human%20directly%20behind%20the%20wheel%20in%20Austin.%20Although%20a%20safety%20monitor%20remains%20in%20the%20front%20passenger%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWayve%20announced%20in%20June%20that%20it%20would%20begin%20testing%20fully%20autonomous%20driving%20in%20London%20with%20Uber%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20co-founded%20by%20Alex%20Kendall%20in%202017%2C%20when%20Alphabet%20was%20nearly%20a%20decade%20into%20robotaxi%20development%20and%20around%20two%20years%20after%20Tesla%20released%20Autopilot%2C%20a%20stripped-down%20version%20of%20FSD%20(Supervised).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20boasts%206%20billion%20miles%20of%20real-world%20driving%20data%20collected%20from%20its%20vehicle%20fleet.%20Wayve%20collects%20data%20from%20multiple%20sources%2C%20including%20its%20own%20fleet%20of%20test%20vehicles%2C%20OEM%20data%2C%20and%20simulated%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20startup%20said%20Wayve's%20AV2.0%20%E2%80%94%20first%20accustomed%20to%20the%20UK's%20right-hand%20driving%20%E2%80%94%20was%20able%20to%20adapt%20to%20US%20roads%20with%20about%20500%20hours%20of%20%26quot%3BUS-specific%20training%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWayve%20announced%20in%20April%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-wayve-partners-with-nissan-on-autonomous-driving-tech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epartnership%20with%20Nissan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20incorporate%20its%20assisted%20driving%20technology%20into%20mass-produced%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20publicly%20said%20that%20the%20company%20is%20in%20talks%20to%20license%20FSD%20to%20major%20automakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20purely%20from%20the%20driving%20experience%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20pinpoint%20where%20a%20passenger%20might%20distinguish%20between%20FSD%20and%20Wayve's%20AV2.0%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwayve-tesla-full-self-driving-comparison-adas-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761996841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69057981c007ca8c27381287%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwayve-tesla-full-self-driving-comparison-adas-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wayve%20is%20developing%20an%20advanced%20driver%20assistance%20system%20that%20is%20akin%20to%20Tesla's%20Full%20Self-Driving%20(Supervised).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwayve-tesla-full-self-driving-comparison-adas-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20GST%20collection%20increases%204.6%25%20to%20%E2%82%B91.96%20trillion%20in%20October%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761996568000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-09%2F05%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1757096890-1857.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-net-gst-kitty-increases-5-6-to-1-95-trillion-in-october-125110100644_1.ht